data.description: Investors Wanted! Add to your rental portfolio or rehab and sell with good After Repair Value. Four bedroom one bath bungalow. Needs TLC but has great potential. Sold As-Is. Unsuitable for FHA or VA loan Ready for Rehab! Motivated seller, NO FHA or VA. Investment opportunity in Mt Healthy. Renovate to rent or resell this 4/1 home in Mt. Healthy. Recent sales and rentals in the area support either option. Being sold as-is, this house does need TLC along with other general updating.  Great opportunity here that just needs some attention. Make it into what you want! Come and see it today!
